### Step 1: Understand the Problem

We are working within the context of proving that evaluating a formula in the combined model on an "old world" (derived from one of the individual models) is equivalent to evaluating it directly in the corresponding individual model. The specific case to prove here is `case mp`, which deals with the `⌈α⌉f` (the boxes) in the formula.

